5 SECTION 7. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
6 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 57-107 of Title 11, unless there
7 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
8 A. Each subsequent resale of property acquired by a land bank
9 under this act must comply with the conditions of this section.
